Package adqlParser.parser

Interface Summary
AdqlParserConstants Token literal values and constants.
 

Class Summary
AdqlParser Parses an ADQL query thanks to the AdqlParser.Query() function.
AdqlParser.JJCalls  
AdqlParserTokenManager Token Manager.
DBConsistency This class is used by AdqlParser to ensure the consistency between an ADQL query and the "database" on which the query must be executed.
DefaultDBConsistency This implementation of DBConsistency can't ensure the consistency with a "database" because it is not linked with any database.
QueryBuilderTools This class lets the AdqlParser to build an object representation of an ADQL query.
SimpleCharStream An implementation of interface CharStream, where the stream is assumed to contain only ASCII characters (without unicode processing).
SQLTranslator  
Token Describes the input token stream.
 

Exception Summary
ParseException This exception is thrown when parse errors are encountered.
 

Error Summary
AdqlParser.LookaheadSuccess  
TokenMgrError Token Manager Error.
